\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Sept 19, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104vkz1665702856823.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/vkz1665702856823.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/vkz1665702856823.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"vkz1665702856823\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n                     \n Type Conversion Rules\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"vkz1665702856823__type_conversion_rules_53488\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"vkz1665702856823__p_d16145e1_d16146e1_d16147e1\">Common conversion rules apply for both implicit and explicit type conversion.</p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"vkz1665702856823__topic_d11702e1_d11703e1_d11704e1_d11705e1_d11706e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d395996e55\">\n                       \n                       Conversion to String\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"vkz1665702856823__table_d1679e1_d1680e1_d1681e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Rules applied when converting to String</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"vkz1665702856823__table_d1679e1_d1680e1_d1681e1__entry__1\">\n Source Data Type\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"vkz1665702856823__table_d1679e1_d1680e1_d1681e1__entry__2\">\n Target Data Type\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"vkz1665702856823__table_d1679e1_d1680e1_d1681e1__entry__3\">\n Result\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vkz1665702856823__table_d1679e1_d1680e1_d1681e1__entry__1\">\n Numeric\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vkz1665702856823__table_d1679e1_d1680e1_d1681e1__entry__2\">\n String\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vkz1665702856823__table_d1679e1_d1680e1_d1681e1__entry__3\">\n Value is converted to String.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vkz1665702856823__table_d1679e1_d1680e1_d1681e1__entry__1\">\n Date\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vkz1665702856823__table_d1679e1_d1680e1_d1681e1__entry__2\">\n String\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vkz1665702856823__table_d1679e1_d1680e1_d1681e1__entry__3\">\n Date is converted to ccyymmdd (the internal format for the date).\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vkz1665702856823__table_d1679e1_d1680e1_d1681e1__entry__1\">\n Time\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vkz1665702856823__table_d1679e1_d1680e1_d1681e1__entry__2\">\n String\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vkz1665702856823__table_d1679e1_d1680e1_d1681e1__entry__3\">\n Time is converted to hhnnsstt (the internal format for the time).\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vkz1665702856823__table_d1679e1_d1680e1_d1681e1__entry__1\">\n Datetime\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vkz1665702856823__table_d1679e1_d1680e1_d1681e1__entry__2\">\n String\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vkz1665702856823__table_d1679e1_d1680e1_d1681e1__entry__3\">\n Datetime is converted to ccyymmddhhnnsstt (the internal format for the datetime).\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vkz1665702856823__table_d1679e1_d1680e1_d1681e1__entry__1\">\n Boolean\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vkz1665702856823__table_d1679e1_d1680e1_d1681e1__entry__2\">\n String\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vkz1665702856823__table_d1679e1_d1680e1_d1681e1__entry__3\">If Boolean is <code class=\"ph codeph\">True</code>, String is\n                           <code class=\"ph codeph\">\"T\"</code>. <p class=\"p\">If Boolean is <code class=\"ph codeph\">False</code>, String is\n                              <code class=\"ph codeph\">\"F\"</code>.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"vkz1665702856823__p_d16148e1_d16149e1_d16150e1\">When converting to Strings, display formats are sometimes applied, but sometimes not. .</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"vkz1665702856823__topic_d11707e1_d11708e1_d11709e1_d11710e1_d11711e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d395996e175\">\n                       \n Conversion to Numeric\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"vkz1665702856823__table_d1682e1_d1683e1_d1684e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 2. </span><span class=\"title\">Rules applied when converting to Numeric</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"vkz1665702856823__table_d1682e1_d1683e1_d1684e1__entry__1\">\n Source Data Type\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"vkz1665702856823__table_d1682e1_d1683e1_d1684e1__entry__2\">\n Target Data Type\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"vkz1665702856823__table_d1682e1_d1683e1_d1684e1__entry__3\">\n Result\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vkz1665702856823__table_d1682e1_d1683e1_d1684e1__entry__1\">\n String\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vkz1665702856823__table_d1682e1_d1683e1_d1684e1__entry__2\">\n Numeric\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vkz1665702856823__table_d1682e1_d1683e1_d1684e1__entry__3\">\n If possible, String is converted to Numeric value.\n <p class=\"p\">Otherwise, Numeric is <code class=\"ph codeph\">0</code>.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vkz1665702856823__table_d1682e1_d1683e1_d1684e1__entry__1\">\n Date\n Time\n Datetime\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vkz1665702856823__table_d1682e1_d1683e1_d1684e1__entry__2\">\n Numeric\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vkz1665702856823__table_d1682e1_d1683e1_d1684e1__entry__3\">\n Converted to a linear number of days.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vkz1665702856823__table_d1682e1_d1683e1_d1684e1__entry__1\">\n Boolean\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vkz1665702856823__table_d1682e1_d1683e1_d1684e1__entry__2\">\n Numeric\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vkz1665702856823__table_d1682e1_d1683e1_d1684e1__entry__3\">If <code class=\"ph codeph\">False</code>, Numeric is\n                           <code class=\"ph codeph\">0</code>. <p class=\"p\">If <code class=\"ph codeph\">True</code>, Numeric is\n                              <code class=\"ph codeph\">1</code>.  </p></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"vkz1665702856823__topic_d11712e1_d11713e1_d11714e1_d11715e1_d11716e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d395996e270\">\n                       \n Conversion to Date\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"vkz1665702856823__table_d1685e1_d1686e1_d1687e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 3. </span><span class=\"title\">Rules applied when converting to Date</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"vkz1665702856823__table_d1685e1_d1686e1_d1687e1__entry__1\">\n Source Data Type\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"vkz1665702856823__table_d1685e1_d1686e1_d1687e1__entry__2\">\n Target Data Type\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"vkz1665702856823__table_d1685e1_d1686e1_d1687e1__entry__3\">\n Result\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vkz1665702856823__table_d1685e1_d1686e1_d1687e1__entry__1\">\n String\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vkz1665702856823__table_d1685e1_d1686e1_d1687e1__entry__2\">\n Date\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vkz1665702856823__table_d1685e1_d1686e1_d1687e1__entry__3\">\n If possible, String is converted to Date using the default Date Format from the current language setup.\n <p class=\"p\">Otherwise, Date is NULL.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vkz1665702856823__table_d1685e1_d1686e1_d1687e1__entry__1\">\n Numeric\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vkz1665702856823__table_d1685e1_d1686e1_d1687e1__entry__2\">\n Date\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vkz1665702856823__table_d1685e1_d1686e1_d1687e1__entry__3\">\n Linear number of days converted to Date.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vkz1665702856823__table_d1685e1_d1686e1_d1687e1__entry__1\">\n Time\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vkz1665702856823__table_d1685e1_d1686e1_d1687e1__entry__2\">\n Date\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vkz1665702856823__table_d1685e1_d1686e1_d1687e1__entry__3\">\n Date is NULL.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vkz1665702856823__table_d1685e1_d1686e1_d1687e1__entry__1\">\n Datetime\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vkz1665702856823__table_d1685e1_d1686e1_d1687e1__entry__2\">\n Date\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vkz1665702856823__table_d1685e1_d1686e1_d1687e1__entry__3\">\n Date part of Datetime value.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vkz1665702856823__table_d1685e1_d1686e1_d1687e1__entry__1\">\n Boolean\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vkz1665702856823__table_d1685e1_d1686e1_d1687e1__entry__2\">\n Date\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vkz1665702856823__table_d1685e1_d1686e1_d1687e1__entry__3\">\n<p class=\"p\">If Boolean is <code class=\"ph codeph\">True</code>, Date is\n                           <code class=\"ph codeph\">01-jan-1900</code>.  </p>\n<p class=\"p\">If Boolean is <code class=\"ph codeph\">False</code>, Date is NULL.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"vkz1665702856823__topic_d11717e1_d11718e1_d11719e1_d11720e1_d11721e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d395996e387\">\n                       \n Conversion to Time\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"vkz1665702856823__table_d1688e1_d1689e1_d1690e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 4. </span><span class=\"title\">Rules applied when converting to Time</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"vkz1665702856823__table_d1688e1_d1689e1_d1690e1__entry__1\">\n Source Data Type\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"vkz1665702856823__table_d1688e1_d1689e1_d1690e1__entry__2\">\n Target Data Type\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"vkz1665702856823__table_d1688e1_d1689e1_d1690e1__entry__3\">\n Result\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vkz1665702856823__table_d1688e1_d1689e1_d1690e1__entry__1\">\n String\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vkz1665702856823__table_d1688e1_d1689e1_d1690e1__entry__2\">\n Time\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vkz1665702856823__table_d1688e1_d1689e1_d1690e1__entry__3\">\n If possible, String is converted to Time using the default Time Format from the current language setup.\n <p class=\"p\">Otherwise, Time is NULL.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vkz1665702856823__table_d1688e1_d1689e1_d1690e1__entry__1\">\n Numeric\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vkz1665702856823__table_d1688e1_d1689e1_d1690e1__entry__2\">\n Time\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vkz1665702856823__table_d1688e1_d1689e1_d1690e1__entry__3\">\n Linear time convert to Time.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vkz1665702856823__table_d1688e1_d1689e1_d1690e1__entry__1\">\n Date\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vkz1665702856823__table_d1688e1_d1689e1_d1690e1__entry__2\">\n Time\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vkz1665702856823__table_d1688e1_d1689e1_d1690e1__entry__3\">Time is <code class=\"ph codeph\">00:00:00:00</code>. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vkz1665702856823__table_d1688e1_d1689e1_d1690e1__entry__1\">\n Datetime\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vkz1665702856823__table_d1688e1_d1689e1_d1690e1__entry__2\">\n Time\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vkz1665702856823__table_d1688e1_d1689e1_d1690e1__entry__3\">\n Time part of Datetime value.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vkz1665702856823__table_d1688e1_d1689e1_d1690e1__entry__1\">\n Boolean\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vkz1665702856823__table_d1688e1_d1689e1_d1690e1__entry__2\">\n Time\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vkz1665702856823__table_d1688e1_d1689e1_d1690e1__entry__3\">Time is <code class=\"ph codeph\">00:00:00:00</code>. </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"vkz1665702856823__topic_d11722e1_d11723e1_d11724e1_d11725e1_d11726e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d395996e496\">\n                       \n Conversion to DateTime\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"vkz1665702856823__table_d1691e1_d1692e1_d1693e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 5. </span><span class=\"title\">Rules applied when converting to DateTime</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"vkz1665702856823__table_d1691e1_d1692e1_d1693e1__entry__1\">\n Source Data Type\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"vkz1665702856823__table_d1691e1_d1692e1_d1693e1__entry__2\">\n Target Data Type\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"vkz1665702856823__table_d1691e1_d1692e1_d1693e1__entry__3\">\n Result\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vkz1665702856823__table_d1691e1_d1692e1_d1693e1__entry__1\">\n String\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vkz1665702856823__table_d1691e1_d1692e1_d1693e1__entry__2\">\n Datetime\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vkz1665702856823__table_d1691e1_d1692e1_d1693e1__entry__3\">\n If possible, String converted to Datetime using the default Datetime format from the current language setup.\n <p class=\"p\">Otherwise, Datetime is NULL.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vkz1665702856823__table_d1691e1_d1692e1_d1693e1__entry__1\">\n Numeric\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vkz1665702856823__table_d1691e1_d1692e1_d1693e1__entry__2\">\n Datetime\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vkz1665702856823__table_d1691e1_d1692e1_d1693e1__entry__3\">\n Linear number of days converted to Datetime.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vkz1665702856823__table_d1691e1_d1692e1_d1693e1__entry__1\">\n Date\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vkz1665702856823__table_d1691e1_d1692e1_d1693e1__entry__2\">\n Datetime\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vkz1665702856823__table_d1691e1_d1692e1_d1693e1__entry__3\">\n Time part of Datetime is NULL.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vkz1665702856823__table_d1691e1_d1692e1_d1693e1__entry__1\">\n Time\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vkz1665702856823__table_d1691e1_d1692e1_d1693e1__entry__2\">\n Datetime\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vkz1665702856823__table_d1691e1_d1692e1_d1693e1__entry__3\">\n Date part of Datetime is NULL.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vkz1665702856823__table_d1691e1_d1692e1_d1693e1__entry__1\">\n Boolean\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vkz1665702856823__table_d1691e1_d1692e1_d1693e1__entry__2\">\n Datetime\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vkz1665702856823__table_d1691e1_d1692e1_d1693e1__entry__3\">\n<p class=\"p\">If Boolean is <code class=\"ph codeph\">True</code>, Datetime is <code class=\"ph codeph\">01-jan-1900\n                              00:00:00:00</code>. </p>\n<p class=\"p\">If Boolean is <code class=\"ph codeph\">False</code>, Datetime is\n                              <code class=\"ph codeph\">00:00:00:00</code> (Date part is NULL).</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"vkz1665702856823__topic_d11727e1_d11728e1_d11729e1_d11730e1_d11731e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d395996e616\">\n                       \n Conversion to Boolean\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"vkz1665702856823__table_d1694e1_d1695e1_d1696e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 6. </span><span class=\"title\">Rules applied when converting to Boolean</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"vkz1665702856823__table_d1694e1_d1695e1_d1696e1__entry__1\">\n Source Data Type\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"vkz1665702856823__table_d1694e1_d1695e1_d1696e1__entry__2\">\n Target Data Type\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"vkz1665702856823__table_d1694e1_d1695e1_d1696e1__entry__3\">\n Result\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vkz1665702856823__table_d1694e1_d1695e1_d1696e1__entry__1\">\n String\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vkz1665702856823__table_d1694e1_d1695e1_d1696e1__entry__2\">\n Boolean\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vkz1665702856823__table_d1694e1_d1695e1_d1696e1__entry__3\">If String starts with <code class=\"ph codeph\">0</code>,\n                           <code class=\"ph codeph\">F</code>, or <code class=\"ph codeph\">N</code>, Boolean is\n                           <code class=\"ph codeph\">False</code>. <p class=\"p\">Otherwise, Boolean is\n                           <code class=\"ph codeph\">True</code>.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vkz1665702856823__table_d1694e1_d1695e1_d1696e1__entry__1\">\n Numeric\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vkz1665702856823__table_d1694e1_d1695e1_d1696e1__entry__2\">\n Boolean\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vkz1665702856823__table_d1694e1_d1695e1_d1696e1__entry__3\">If Numeric is <code class=\"ph codeph\">0</code>, Boolean is\n                           <code class=\"ph codeph\">False</code>. <p class=\"p\">If Numeric is not <code class=\"ph codeph\">0</code>, Boolean\n                           is <code class=\"ph codeph\">True</code>.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vkz1665702856823__table_d1694e1_d1695e1_d1696e1__entry__1\">\n Date\n Time\n Datetime\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vkz1665702856823__table_d1694e1_d1695e1_d1696e1__entry__2\">\n Boolean\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vkz1665702856823__table_d1694e1_d1695e1_d1696e1__entry__3\">If Date, Time, or Datetime is NULL, Boolean is\n                           <code class=\"ph codeph\">False</code>. <p class=\"p\">If Date, Time, or Datetime is not NULL,\n                           Boolean is <code class=\"ph codeph\">True</code>.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2533064\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2533064\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Type Conversion Rules Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Sept 19, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Type Conversion Rules Common conversion rules apply for both implicit and explicit type conversion. Conversion to String Table 1. Rules applied when converting to String Source Data Type Target Data Type Result Numeric String Value is converted to String. Date String Date is converted to ccyymmdd (the internal format for the date). Time String Time is converted to hhnnsstt (the internal format for the time). Datetime String Datetime is converted to ccyymmddhhnnsstt (the internal format for the datetime). Boolean String If Boolean is True , String is \"T\" . If Boolean is False , String is \"F\" . When converting to Strings, display formats are sometimes applied, but sometimes not. . Conversion to Numeric Table 2. Rules applied when converting to Numeric Source Data Type Target Data Type Result String Numeric If possible, String is converted to Numeric value. Otherwise, Numeric is 0 . Date Time Datetime Numeric Converted to a linear number of days. Boolean Numeric If False , Numeric is 0 . If True , Numeric is 1 . Conversion to Date Table 3. Rules applied when converting to Date Source Data Type Target Data Type Result String Date If possible, String is converted to Date using the default Date Format from the current language setup. Otherwise, Date is NULL. Numeric Date Linear number of days converted to Date. Time Date Date is NULL. Datetime Date Date part of Datetime value. Boolean Date If Boolean is True , Date is 01-jan-1900 . If Boolean is False , Date is NULL. Conversion to Time Table 4. Rules applied when converting to Time Source Data Type Target Data Type Result String Time If possible, String is converted to Time using the default Time Format from the current language setup. Otherwise, Time is NULL. Numeric Time Linear time convert to Time. Date Time Time is 00:00:00:00 . Datetime Time Time part of Datetime value. Boolean Time Time is 00:00:00:00 . Conversion to DateTime Table 5. Rules applied when converting to DateTime Source Data Type Target Data Type Result String Datetime If possible, String converted to Datetime using the default Datetime format from the current language setup. Otherwise, Datetime is NULL. Numeric Datetime Linear number of days converted to Datetime. Date Datetime Time part of Datetime is NULL. Time Datetime Date part of Datetime is NULL. Boolean Datetime If Boolean is True , Datetime is 01-jan-1900 00:00:00:00 . If Boolean is False , Datetime is 00:00:00:00 (Date part is NULL). Conversion to Boolean Table 6. Rules applied when converting to Boolean Source Data Type Target Data Type Result String Boolean If String starts with 0 , F , or N , Boolean is False . Otherwise, Boolean is True . Numeric Boolean If Numeric is 0 , Boolean is False . If Numeric is not 0 , Boolean is True . Date Time Datetime Boolean If Date, Time, or Datetime is NULL, Boolean is False . If Date, Time, or Datetime is not NULL, Boolean is True . Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}